    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a buyer looking for a project or a parts car. The engine has significant oil leaks and a noticeable knock, suggesting a need for a major overhaul or replacement. Cosmetically, the exterior has several large dents, peeling clear coat on the hood, and some structural rust starting near the wheel wells. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional air conditioning system. Please expect to tow this vehicle as it is not currently reliable for long-distance driving.",
