    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready for its next adventure with you! I\u2019ve kept up with the basics, and it still feels super smooth on the road. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver without the brand-new price tag. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit utilizes the Getrag six-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement through the gears. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the Vanos system has been professionally serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The factory M-Variable limited-slip differential provides predictable power delivery under load. While the aesthetics show honest patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and dampers. This is a driver-focused example that prioritizes drivetrain performance and structural integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Engine runs well. Interior is clean. Title is clear. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect blend of performance and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a beautiful factory shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the leather seating is supple and free of cracks, and all interior electronics\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and responsive, benefiting from a documented history of on-time synthetic oil changes and a recent professional tune-up. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a turn-key car that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
